      "text": "And it takes a very patient parent to make them stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14190.0,
      "end_time": 16880.0,
      "text": "When it comes to TV and movies, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16880.0,
      "end_time": 20473.0,
      "text": "a director may actually want a baby to cry on command."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23100.0,
      "end_time": 24460.0,
      "text": "And this requires hiring someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24460.0,
      "end_time": 26151.0,
      "text": "with a special set of skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31220.0,
      "end_time": 32560.0,
      "text": "That's Elaine Hall."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32560.000000000004,
      "end_time": 36180.0,
      "text": "She's what's known in Hollywood as a baby wrangler."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36180.0,
      "end_time": 40700.0,
      "text": "Elaine Hall: A baby wrangler is a interpreter"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40700.0,
      "end_time": 44880.0,
      "text": "between what the director wants a young child to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45747.0,
      "end_time": 47540.0,
      "text": "in front of a camera."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47540.0,
      "end_time": 49830.0,
      "text": "Narrator: She's worked with infants and young children"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49830.0,
      "end_time": 54140.0,
      "text": "on a variety of commercials, TV shows, and movies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54140.0,
      "end_time": 57600.0,
      "text": "like \"The Flintstones,\" \"Grace Under Fire,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57600.0,
      "end_time": 59620.0,
      "text": "and \"Akeelah tnd the Bee.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59620.0,
      "end_time": 63540.0,
      "text": "First off, where do these crying babies come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63540.0,
      "end_time": 66200.0,
      "text": "Babies, just like adult actors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66200.0,
      "end_time": 67619.0,
      "text": "come from casting calls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67620.0,
      "end_time": 69960.0,
      "text": "but they're only legally allowed to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69960.0,
      "end_time": 72100.0,
      "text": "for four hours a day on set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72100.0,
      "end_time": 75350.0,
      "text": "so there's a simple trick used to extend their camera time."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75350.0,
      "end_time": 80350.0,
      "text": "Hall: Very often, when you see a TV show or a film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80560.0,
      "end_time": 84430.0,
      "text": "twins are used to play one role."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84430.0,
      "end_time": 86190.0,
      "text": "Narrator: There's also a few other rules in place"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86190.0,
      "end_time": 87550.0,
      "text": "when using young actors."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87550.0,
      "end_time": 89270.0,
      "text": "Hall: For every set that has a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89270.0,
      "end_time": 91710.0,
      "text": "there's a studio teacher on the set."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91710.0,
      "end_time": 96710.0,
      "text": "For infants, there must be a studio teacher and a nurse."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97240.0,
      "end_time": 99500.0,
      "text": "Narrator: For non-crying scenes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99500.0,
      "end_time": 100820.0,
      "text": "working with babies and young children"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100820.0,
      "end_time": 102929.0,
      "text": "involves making it fun for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102930.0,
      "end_time": 104550.0,
      "text": "Hall: Everything was made into a game."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104550.0,
      "end_time": 109500.0,
      "text": "I would put on the lens of the camera,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109500.0,
      "end_time": 111160.0,
      "text": "funny faces on the lens,"
