    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 111160.0,
      "end_time": 113590.0,
      "text": "when they needed to make direct eye contact."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113590.0,
      "end_time": 115400.0,
      "text": "I would be behind the camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115400.0,
      "end_time": 117480.0,
      "text": "on every scene, making them laugh."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117480.0,
      "end_time": 119930.0,
      "text": "Narrator: But for crying, it's a whole different story."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119930.0,
      "end_time": 121970.0,
      "text": "Elaine uses a special technique."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121970.0,
      "end_time": 124750.0,
      "text": "Hall: What I do to get babies to cry is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124750.0,
      "end_time": 127170.0,
      "text": "I start to cry myself."
