    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127170.0,
      "end_time": 129940.0,
      "text": "For example, I'll go, \"Wahhhh!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141750.0,
      "end_time": 142890.0,
      "text": "And the baby will start to cry."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142890.0,
      "end_time": 147890.0,
      "text": "When a baby, even an infant, hears another baby cry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149760.0,
      "end_time": 154253.0,
      "text": "the infant or the baby will start to cry themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155160.0,
      "end_time": 158150.0,
      "text": "This is an example of empathy."
