    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 158150.0,
      "end_time": 159710.0,
      "text": "It's pretty instantaneous."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159710.0,
      "end_time": 162870.0,
      "text": "Narrator: She used this technique in \"Akeelah And The Bee.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162870.0,
      "end_time": 165400.0,
      "text": "In this scene, Akeelah's sister brings her baby"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165400.0,
      "end_time": 167893.0,
      "text": "to the event, and it starts to cry."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172970.0,
      "end_time": 176780.0,
      "text": "And her technique has never failed, so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 176780.0,
      "end_time": 179610.0,
      "text": "Hall: My success rate is 100 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179610.0,
      "end_time": 181790.0,
      "text": "Narrator: She says she's heard of other baby wranglers"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 181790.0,
      "end_time": 185530.0,
      "text": "using questionable techniques like placing bad odors"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185530.0,
      "end_time": 189180.0,
      "text": "in front of the child or making a loud noise."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189180.0,
      "end_time": 191500.0,
      "text": "But according to Elaine, these sorts of methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191500.0,
      "end_time": 194510.0,
      "text": "may be harmful to the child, and should be avoided."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 194510.0,
      "end_time": 197489.0,
      "text": "If the baby's face doesn't need to be shown on camera,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 197490.0,
      "end_time": 199933.0,
      "text": "oftentimes, they'll use a doll instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 203690.0,
      "end_time": 207190.0,
      "text": "Once it's crying, how do you get the baby to stop?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207190.0,
      "end_time": 209579.0,
      "text": "Hall: When I stop crying, and then I'll look at the baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 209580.0,
      "end_time": 212690.0,
      "text": "and assure the baby that everything's safe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 212690.0,
      "end_time": 215140.0,
      "text": "I'm okay, she's okay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 215140.0,
      "end_time": 218380.0,
      "text": "then, very quickly, a baby will stop crying."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 218380.0,
      "end_time": 220480.0,
      "text": "Narrator: She may also use rattles and bells"
